{"word":"H5712 - עֵדָה - ʻêdâh - ay-daw' - Assembly","slug":"H5712","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">עֵדָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʻêdâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ay-daw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Assembly"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E2;&#x05D3;&#x05D4; - &#x201B;e&#x0302;da&#x0302;h</b> - <i>ay-daw'</i><p/>Feminine of <a href=\"#/H5707\">H5707</a> in the original sense of <i>fixture</i>; a stated <i>assemblage</i> (specifically a <i>concourse</i>, or generally a <i>family</i> or <i>crowd</i>): - assembly, company, congregation, multitude, people, swarm. Compare <a href=\"#/H5713\">H5713</a>."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3259\">H3259</a>, <a href=\"#/H3260\">H3260</a>, <a href=\"#/H4150\">H4150</a>, <a href=\"#/H4151\">H4151</a>, <a href=\"#/H4152\">H4152</a>, <a href=\"#/H5129\">H5129</a>"}]}